des: Mindset 365 is your daily dose of inspiration. In many ways it is a collection of quotes but in actuality it is a collection of perspectives from the greatest minds human kind has ever seen from the wisest philosophers to the most visionary tech entrepreneurs. Our host offers a modern spin to these quotes through the lens of a young professional seeking personal growth each and every day.
